1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new loss function for bounding box regression, which is a key component of many machine learning-based object detection algorithms. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Object detection is a common task in AI, and the paper proposes a new approach to improve the performance of object detection algorithms. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) - Object detection is also an important task in robotics, and the proposed approach could potentially be applied to improve the performance of robotic vision systems. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - Object detection is a common task in multimedia applications, and the proposed approach could potentially be applied to improve the performance of multimedia systems that rely on object detection.
